        <text>
            <body>
                    <p>Ego <persName key="d1e11165" xml:id="d1e128802">Dominicus, major <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282515" xml:id="d1e128804" corresp="ville de Dijon">communie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#96489" xml:id="d1e128806" corresp="Dijon (Côte-d'Or, Dijon)">Divionis</placeName>
                            </orgName>
                        </persName>, omnibus notum facio presentibus pariter et futuris quod fratres
                        de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e128809" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fon<lb n="2" break="no" />teneto</orgName> emerunt a <persName key="d1e11172" xml:id="d1e128814">Johanne</persName> et <persName key="d1e11178" xml:id="d1e128817">Willermo de Divione</persName>, hominibus suis, pratum suum quod est
                        situm subtus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325274" xml:id="d1e128820" corresp="Farverni">Farverni</placeName>
                        <lb n="3" /> in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324899" xml:id="d1e128825" corresp="Lamponne (Côte-d'Or, Chevigny-Saint-Sauveur)">pratea de
                            Lampone</placeName>, necnon et <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325235" xml:id="d1e128828" corresp="vineam eorum que dicitur Milonis">vineam eorum que dicitur Milonis</placeName> et est
                        apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324342" xml:id="d1e128831" corresp="Pouilly-en-Auxois (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">
                            <foreign>Polli</foreign>
                        </placeName>, que continet in se <choice>
                            <sic>apertum</sic>
                            <corr>arpentum</corr>
                        </choice>
                        <lb n="4" /> et dimidium, videlicet pro centum quinquaginta libris
                        divionensium. Hoc totum laudavit <persName key="d1e11184" xml:id="d1e128842">Maria, uxor predicti Johannis</persName>. Idem <lb n="5" /> etiam
                            <persName key="d1e11190" xml:id="d1e128848">Johannes</persName> et
                        superius nominata <persName key="d1e11196" xml:id="d1e128851">uxor ipsius
                            Maria</persName> vendiderunt eisdem fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e128854" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> aliam vineam
                        de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324342" xml:id="d1e128857" corresp="Pouilly-en-Auxois (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">
                            <hi rend="italic">Polli</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <lb n="6" /> que similiter continet in se arpentum et dimidium pro quater
                        viginti libris divionensium. Hoc etiam filii ipsorum lau<lb n="7" break="no" />daverunt, <persName key="d1e11202" xml:id="d1e128865">Petrus</persName>
                        scilicet et <persName key="d1e11209" xml:id="d1e128868">Johannes</persName>,
                        necnon et <persName key="d1e11215" xml:id="d1e128871">Willermus, frater
                            sepedicti Johannis</persName>, hoc laudavit. Nos vero ad memoriam <lb n="8" /> hujus rei et munimen, ne quis decetero predictos fratres
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e128876" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        super hoc molestaret, presens scriptum sigillo <lb n="9" />
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282515" xml:id="d1e128881" corresp="ville de Dijon">communie Divionis</orgName>
                        roboravimus. Actum anno verbi incarnati millesimo ducentesimo
                        terciodecimo.</p>
                
